title: Sameer Gehlaut resigns as Indiabulls Housing Finance's Non-Executive Director - Moneycontrol
content: Sameer Gehlaut resigns as Indiabulls Housing Finance's Non-Executive Director  Moneycontrol
description: Sameer Gehlaut will also be resigning from the Board of the Company by the end of the current financial year, March 31, 2022.
